snippet.title: The Deadly Dungeons of Baron Backslash
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage from the Deadly Dungeons of Baron Backslash - a fiendishly challenging retro pixel-art dungeon escape game. Play it now at http://www.baronbackslash.com, or at itch.io: https://redmarsdigital.itch.io/baronbackslash

Runs in the browser, needs a keyboard - and completely free.

If you enjoy it let me know, and give me the encouragement to add more content!
